      <div>
        <p class="font-mono font-bold text-primary dark:text-accent text-lg">DaGint</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Professional IT support. We fix it so you can focus.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Quick links</p>
